#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprf.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.elliprf"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:1 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the first kind."
msgstr "第一类完全对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:3 of
msgid "The function RF is defined as [1]_"
msgstr "函数 RF 定义为 [1]_"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:5 of
msgid ""
"R_{\\mathrm{F}}(x, y, z) =\n"
"   \\frac{1}{2} \\int_0^{+\\infty} [(t + x) (t + y) (t + z)]^{-1/2} dt"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprf.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:10
#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:14
#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:18 of
msgid ""
"Real or complex input parameters. `x`, `y`, or `z` can be any number in "
"the complex plane cut along the negative real axis, but at most one of "
"them can be zero."
msgstr ""
"实数或复数输入参数。`x`、`y` 或 `z` 可以是沿负实轴切割的复平面中的任意"
"数字，但最多只能有一个为零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:22 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprf.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:25 of
msgid ""
"**R** -- Value of the integral. If all of `x`, `y`, and `z` are real, the"
" return value is real. Otherwise, the return value is complex."
msgstr ""
"**R** -- 积分值。如果 `x`、`y` 和 `z` 都是实数，则返回值为实数。否则，"
"返回值为复数。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprf.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:32 of
msgid "Degenerate symmetric integral."
msgstr "退化的对称积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprd`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:35 of
msgid "Symmetric elliptic integral of the second kind."
msgstr "第二类对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:37 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprg`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:38 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the second kind."
msgstr "第二类完全对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:40 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprj`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:41 of
msgid "Symmetric elliptic integral of the third kind."
msgstr "第三类对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:44 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:45 of
msgid ""
"The code implements Carlson's algorithm based on the duplication theorems"
" and series expansion up to the 7th order (cf.: "
"https://dlmf.nist.gov/19.36.i) and the AGM algorithm for the complete "
"integral. [2]_"
msgstr ""
"代码实现了基于倍增定理和最高至七阶级数展开的 Carlson 算法（参见：https://"
"dlmf.nist.gov/19.36.i）以及用于完全积分的 AGM 算法。[2]_"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:51 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:52 of
msgid ""
"B. C. Carlson, ed., Chapter 19 in \"Digital Library of Mathematical "
"Functions,\" NIST, US Dept. of Commerce. https://dlmf.nist.gov/19.16.E1"
msgstr ""
"B. C. Carlson 编，《数学函数数字图书馆》第19章，NIST，美国商务部。https:/"
"/dlmf.nist.gov/19.16.E1"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprf:55 of
msgid ""
"B. C. Carlson, \"Numerical computation of real or complex elliptic "
"integrals,\" Numer. Algorithm, vol. 10, no. 1, pp. 13-26, 1995. "
"https://arxiv.org/abs/math/9409227 https://doi.org/10.1007/BF02198293"
msgstr ""
"B. C. Carlson, “实数或复数椭圆积分的数值计算,” Numer. Algorithm, 卷 10,"
" 编号 1, 页 13-26, 1995. https://arxiv.org/abs/math/9409227 https://doi."
"org/10.1007/BF02198293"

